urlText: Buses replace trains between Lidcombe and Strathfield. Travel to and from the City via Bankstown or the Airport
content:
Saturday 6 and Sunday 7 April
  • Buses replace trains between Lidcombe and Strathfield.
  • If you are travelling to the City you can change at:
    - Glenfield for trains via the Airport
    - Liverpool or Lidcombe for trains via Bankstown

  • If travelling to Flemington, Homebush or Strathfield, change at Lidcombe for a bus.
  • Trackwork buses do not leave from Olympic Park.
  • Trains run to a changed timetable between:
    - Leppington and Olympic Park via Granville
    - Leppington and Richmond
    - Liverpool or Lidcombe and the City via Bankstown
    - Glenfield and the City via the Airport
    - Strathfield and the City
    - Ashfield and the City, then Lindfield

  • Replacement buses may be impacted by driver shortages. We are doing all we can to minimise the impact to your journey and provide a safe service, however cancellations or delays may occur.
  • Plan your trip before you travel for up-to-date real time information. You can also subscribe to planned trackwork alerts.
Bus routes
67T1 Lidcombe, then Flemington, Homebush, Strathfield and return
68T1 Lidcombe, then Strathfield and return

urlText: Major Event Buses operating for the Sydney Royal Easter Show
content:
Sydney Olympic Park Major Event Buses will run each day during the Sydney Royal Easter Show from Friday 22 March to Tuesday 2 April.
 
Travel on the Major Event Buses is included in the cost of tickets to the Easter Show only. Attendees do not need to tap on and off, simply show your Show ticket to the driver when boarding buses.
 
Buses run every 10 to 20 minutes, timetables vary on weekdays and weekends during the Easter Show and are subject to traffic conditions.
 
Buses to Olympic Park will run from early morning until around 3pm. Return buses will start leaving Olympic Park from 2pm each day, with the last bus leaving at 10.30pm each night.
 
For more information on transport options to the event, see the Easter Show event page.
